cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the application of deep convolutional neural networks for the classification of breast masses in mammograms. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging (cs.MM) which is also a likely sub-category.
